author: Melanie Kelly
title: Melanie Kelly
text: Still waiting on one item over a week later. Phoned Swords branch, extremely unhelpful staff member, his only response was the item was not in stock and he didn't know how long it would take. This was after five minutes of me explaining a very simple situation to him. Order number and part number was given.
